{
  "video_id": "2CenaMdSVRA",
  "title": "Resident Evil 2 Review",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 819.0,
      "end_time": 3485.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 6101.0,
      "end_time": 8220.0,
      "text": "(zombie growls)"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8220.0,
      "end_time": 10680.0,
      "text": "- [Daemon] Now this is how you remake a classic."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10680.0,
      "end_time": 13590.0,
      "text": "Capcom didn&#39;t just update 1998&#39;s Resident Evil 2"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 13590.0,
      "end_time": 15347.0,
      "text": "with modern graphics and controls."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 15347.0,
      "end_time": 18340.0,
      "text": "They started from scratch to craft a modern feeling game"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18340.0,
      "end_time": 20950.0,
      "text": "that expertly reanimates the horrifying atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20950.0,
      "end_time": 22650.0,
      "text": "and moments of extreme tension"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 22650.0,
      "end_time": 24720.0,
      "text": "that made the original so revered."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24720.0,
      "end_time": 26750.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s not a ton of content here"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26750.0,
      "end_time": 28810.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ve enjoyed nearly every gory minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 28810.0,
      "end_time": 31843.0,
      "text": "of my return to Leon and Claire&#39;s shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31843.0,
      "end_time": 34510.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 39380.0,
      "end_time": 42360.0,
      "text": "20 years is a long time, long enough that I&#39;d forgotten"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 42360.0,
      "end_time": 44360.0,
      "text": "nearly everything about Resident Evil 2,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 44360.0,
      "end_time": 46890.0,
      "text": "other than that I&#39;d loved it back in the age"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 46900.0,
      "end_time": 47660.0,
      "text": "of the first Playstation."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47660.0,
      "end_time": 49669.0,
      "text": "So I got to experience it much as many of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 49670.0,
      "end_time": 51210.0,
      "text": "playing for the first time will."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 51210.0,
      "end_time": 53500.0,
      "text": "But viewed side by side it&#39;s apparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 53500.0,
      "end_time": 55330.0,
      "text": "what an enormous improvement this remake is."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 55330.0,
      "end_time": 57140.0,
      "text": "The horror heightening lighting affects"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 57140.0,
      "end_time": 59220.0,
      "text": "and convincingly terrified facial animations"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59220.0,
      "end_time": 60510.0,
      "text": "are especially impressive"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60510.0,
      "end_time": 62750.0,
      "text": "and the satisfyingly dismemberable zombies"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 62750.0,
      "end_time": 65349.0,
      "text": "are the best looking undead I&#39;ve ever seen in a game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 65349.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66390.0,
      "text": "and the juiciest."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 66390.0,
      "end_time": 67950.0,
      "text": "I love the way they lurch around"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 67950.0,
      "end_time": 68960.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d venture a guess"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 68960.0,
      "end_time": 70410.0,
      "text": "that the designers were heavily inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 70410.0,
      "end_time": 72810.0,
      "text": "by the tar man from Return of the Living Dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 72810.0,
      "end_time": 75200.0,
      "text": "Some events have been rearranged or expanded upon"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 75200.0,
      "end_time": 77660.0,
      "text": "and there are some surprising twists I didn&#39;t remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 77660.0,
      "end_time": 79130.0,
      "text": "But this is a mostly loyal remake"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 79130.0,
      "end_time": 81960.0,
      "text": "of the suitably dark and twisted story of Resident Evil 2."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 81960.0,
      "end_time": 83949.0,
      "text": "Our heroes meanwhile are likable enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 83950.0,
      "end_time": 86600.0,
      "text": "but two-dimensional in their unwavering heroism."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 86600.0,
      "end_time": 87750.0,
      "text": "That makes &#39;em a bit dull,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 87750.0,
      "end_time": 89360.0,
      "text": "whereas a couple of the side characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 89360.0,
      "end_time": 91210.0,
      "text": "are more charismatic and interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 92820.0,
      "end_time": 94100.0,
      "text": "- [Leon] Jesus."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 94100.0,
      "end_time": 95919.0,
      "text": "- [Daemon] Whether you play as Leon or Claire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 95920.0,
      "end_time": 98880.0,
      "text": "exploring dark hallways, solving silly but fun puzzles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 98880.0,
      "end_time": 102429.0,
      "text": "and blasting zombies all remains just as enjoyable today."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 102430.0,
      "end_time": 104730.0,
      "text": "Raccoon City is divided into three large areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 104730.0,
      "end_time": 107200.0,
      "text": "which also serve as the stories acts."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 107200.0,
      "end_time": 109300.0,
      "text": "Charting each area, learning the lay of the land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 109300.0,
      "end_time": 111509.0,
      "text": "and eventually overcoming the obstacles in your way"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 111510.0,
      "end_time": 113246.0,
      "text": "really never gets old."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 113246.0,
      "end_time": 115913.0,
      "text": "(stairs rumble)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 118790.0,
      "text": "Capcom clearly doesn&#39;t expect us"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 118790.0,
      "end_time": 120850.0,
      "text": "to be running and gunning like superheroes."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 120850.0,
      "end_time": 122839.0,
      "text": "The bloody beating heart of Resident Evil"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 122840.0,
      "end_time": 125190.0,
      "text": "is in careful inventory and management"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 125190.0,
      "end_time": 127440.0,
      "text": "and challenging, skin of your teeth survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 127440.0,
      "end_time": 129829.0,
      "text": "It always seems like I was just barely scraping by"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 129830.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131450.0,
      "text": "with enough bullets and healing items"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 131450.0,
      "end_time": 134549.0,
      "text": "which created a real feeling that I was in constant danger."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 134550.0,
      "end_time": 135760.0,
      "text": "That tension has been elevated"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 135760.0,
      "end_time": 137817.0,
      "text": "by the commendable sound design."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 137818.0,
      "end_time": 139930.0,
      "text": "- [Claire] What the hell is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 139930.0,
      "end_time": 141670.0,
      "text": "- [Daemon] Resident Evil 2 gets horror atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 141670.0,
      "end_time": 143220.0,
      "text": "like nobody&#39;s business."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 143220.0,
      "end_time": 144403.0,
      "text": "At the same time, the remake"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 144403.0,
      "end_time": 146440.0,
      "text": "is a little more merciful than the original."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 146440.0,
      "end_time": 147550.0,
      "text": "We get modern conveniences"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 147550.0,
      "end_time": 150700.0,
      "text": "like being able to save your progress at any typewriter"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 150700.0,
      "end_time": 151680.0,
      "text": "and maps which automatically update"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 151680.0,
      "end_time": 154576.0,
      "text": "to let you know if a room has been cleared of items."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 154576.0,
      "end_time": 157700.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 157700.0,
      "end_time": 159390.0,
      "text": "The real chiller in the first two thirds of the campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 159390.0,
      "end_time": 161350.0,
      "text": "is the Tyrant super zombie."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 161350.0,
      "end_time": 163900.0,
      "text": "He appears early on to stalk you"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 163900.0,
      "end_time": 165620.0,
      "text": "and his emotionless face and steady unstoppable gait"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 165620.0,
      "end_time": 167500.0,
      "text": "makes him Resident Evil&#39;s worthy counterpart"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 167500.0,
      "end_time": 169850.0,
      "text": "to Jason Voorhees or Michael Myers."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 169850.0,
      "end_time": 172799.0,
      "text": "Hearing his relentless footsteps getting louder and louder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 173980.0,
      "end_time": 176490.0,
      "text": "knowing there is nothing I can do to stop him"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 176500.0,
      "end_time": 178700.0,
      "text": "filled me with a true sense of dread."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 178700.0,
      "end_time": 180490.0,
      "text": "Eventually though, he becomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 180500.0,
      "end_time": 182760.0,
      "text": "more of an obnoxious inconvenience than a fear factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 182760.0,
      "end_time": 185900.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re trying to solve a puzzle and advance the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 185900.0,
      "end_time": 186490.0,
      "text": "it would&#39;ve been nice if the big lug"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 186490.0,
      "end_time": 188940.0,
      "text": "would just take a hint and reside somewhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 190360.0,
      "end_time": 191930.0,
      "text": "(screaming)"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 191930.0,
      "end_time": 193900.0,
      "text": "I finished Leon&#39;s campaign in eight hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 193900.0,
      "end_time": 195830.0,
      "text": "that seemed to fly by a little too quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 195830.0,
      "end_time": 197450.0,
      "text": "and eagerly jumped into Claire&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 197450.0,
      "end_time": 199989.0,
      "text": "for what I expected to be a completely different perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 199990.0,
      "end_time": 201570.0,
      "text": "on that faithful evenings events"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 201570.0,
      "end_time": 204150.0,
      "text": "after the two are separated in the story&#39;s opening moments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 204150.0,
      "end_time": 205970.0,
      "text": "but I was disappointed to find that she took"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 205970.0,
      "end_time": 208840.0,
      "text": "an extremely similar path, met the same people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 208840.0,
      "end_time": 211750.0,
      "text": "solved the same puzzles, and fought the same bosses."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 211750.0,
      "end_time": 213300.0,
      "text": "You do have to adapt your tactics"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 213300.0,
      "end_time": 214970.0,
      "text": "and learn to use a new set of weaponry"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 214970.0,
      "end_time": 217400.0,
      "text": "and each hero does meet a unique, important person"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 217400.0,
      "end_time": 220700.0,
      "text": "that causes them to deviate from the shared path for a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 220700.0,
      "end_time": 222910.0,
      "text": "It turns out the other perspective does exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 222910.0,
      "end_time": 223970.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s confusingly hidden"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 223970.0,
      "end_time": 226359.0,
      "text": "behind each character&#39;s second game mode."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 226360.0,
      "end_time": 227830.0,
      "text": "You have to play through as Leon once"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 227830.0,
      "end_time": 229480.0,
      "text": "to unlock the second version as Leon"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 229480.0,
      "end_time": 230880.0,
      "text": "and the same for Claire."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 230880.0,
      "end_time": 231980.0,
      "text": "By the time I figured this out"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 231980.0,
      "end_time": 234290.0,
      "text": "I had already played through the same campaign twice"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 234290.0,
      "end_time": 236900.0,
      "text": "but at least I&#39;m finally seeing some new areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 236900.0,
      "end_time": 238280.0,
      "text": "and there is the promise of an alternate ending."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 238280.0,
      "end_time": 240700.0,
      "text": "The way Capcom laid out these two versions"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 240700.0,
      "end_time": 242179.0,
      "text": "of the campaign is baffling."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 242179.0,
      "end_time": 245270.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 245270.0,
      "end_time": 247510.0,
      "text": "Capcom did a fantastic job of resurrecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 247510.0,
      "end_time": 249760.0,
      "text": "all the best part of the classic Resident Evil 2"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 249760.0,
      "end_time": 253299.0,
      "text": "and making them look, sound, and play like a 2019 game."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 253300.0,
      "end_time": 254133.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re of the mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 254133.0,
      "end_time": 256300.0,
      "text": "that the series had lost its way for awhile there"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 256290.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258429.00000000003,
      "text": "this game is very much a return to form."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 258430.0,
      "end_time": 259970.0,
      "text": "The zombie combat is satisfying"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 259970.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261580.00000000003,
      "text": "and exploring the dilapidated ruins"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 261579.0,
      "end_time": 263380.0,
      "text": "of Raccoon City is a thrill."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 263380.0,
      "end_time": 265230.0,
      "text": "The one big letdown is that Capcom"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 265230.0,
      "end_time": 268550.0,
      "text": "unintuitively hides the alternate perspective content."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 268550.0,
      "end_time": 270100.0,
      "text": "Though whichever character you play as,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 270100.0,
      "end_time": 271120.0,
      "text": "the experience of playing through"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 271120.0,
      "end_time": 273500.0,
      "text": "the new Resident Evil 2 for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 273500.0,
      "end_time": 276230.0,
      "text": "establishes a new standard for remaking classic games."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 276230.0,
      "end_time": 277290.0,
      "text": "For more on Resident Evil"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 277290.0,
      "end_time": 279150.0,
      "text": "check out the first 15 minutes of gameplay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 279150.0,
      "end_time": 281109.0,
      "text": "our comparison of the remake and the original,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 281110.0,
      "end_time": 282890.0,
      "text": "and our favorite moments from the series."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 282890.0,
      "end_time": 285613.0,
      "text": "And for everything else stick with us right here at IGN."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 285613.0,
      "end_time": 288213.0,
      "text": "(screams)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 288213.0,
      "end_time": 290880.0,
      "text": "(ominous music)"
    }
  ]
}